パッケージ com.shimizukenta.secs.gem

Implementation package providing GEM (SEMI-E30) interface.
  • インタフェースの概要
    インタフェース 説明
    Clock
    This interface is implementation of Clock in GEM (SEMI-E30).
    DynamicCollectionEvent
    This interface is implementation of Enable-CEID in GEM (SEMI-E30).
    DynamicEventReportConfig
    This interface is implementation of Dynamic-Event-Report-Configuration in GEM (SEMI-E30).
    DynamicLink
    This interface is implementation of Event-Report-Link in GEM (SEMI-E30).
    DynamicReport
    This interface is implementation of Define-Report in GEM (SEMI-E30).
    Gem
    This interface is implementation of GEM (SEMI-E30, partially).
    GemConfig
    This interface is GEM config.
